de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.core.analysis

Class AnalyserBlackboardView

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.core.analysis.AnalyserBlackboardView

  • public class AnalyserBlackboardView
extends java.lang.Object
    View of the Blackboard designed to be used by ProposedExpressionAnalyser. Reading information and adding proposed expressions to the Blackboard is supported.
    See Also:
    for information about Blackboard views.
